    "body" : "<h2>Add <code>catalina.jar</code></h2>\n<p>Just after posting this, it occurred to me that Tomcat doesn't have access to the actual JAR file.</p>\n<p>So, I copied the <code>catalina.jar</code> file into my project, added as library. Now I can step through the code, just like everything else.</p>\n"
